                "summer_19": "...",
                "summer_26": "...",
                "spring_Krobus": "It's 'spring' now, isn't it? I can smell the peppery aroma of wild horseradish.",
                "spring_1": "What's your plan for the new year, @?",
                "spring_2": "KROBUS NEEDS SOMETHING TO SAY!$6",
                "spring_5": "...",
                "spring_12": "...",
                "spring_19": "...",
                "spring_23": "You should go to the flower dance tomorrow! I look forward to hearing your observations.",
                "spring_26": "...",
                "summer_Krobus": "You call this time of year 'summer', right? The warmth and humidity is nice, but I wish it wasn't so sunny.",
                "summer_1": "I get sunburnt very easily, so I need to be careful this time of year.",
                "summer_4": "I tried some of your 'sunscreen,' but it made my skin peel horribly... I must be allergic.$s",
                "summer_8": "Mmm... what's that lovely smell? You must've been sweating all night...$h",
                "summer_15": "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies.#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of them. It's good protein!$h",
                "fall_Krobus": "It's been feeling a bit cooler lately, with a musty smell. You call this time of year 'fall', correct?",
                "fall_1": "KROBUS NEEDS SOMETHING TO SAY!$6",
                "fall_2": "KROBUS NEEDS SOMETHING TO SAY!$6",
                "fall_5": "...",
                "fall_6": "KROBUS NEEDS SOMETHING TO SAY!$6",
                "fall_8": "I don't feel like doing anything today.",
                "fall_12": "...",
                "fall_15": "Have you figured out what you're going to use for your grange display tomorrow?",
                "fall_19": "...",
                "fall_20": "",
                "fall_24": "",
                "fall_26": "...",
                "fall_27": "$c .5# Today I will attend the Festival of the Mundane with my kindred. You are welcome to accompany me, but we should probably get you a disguise just in case.$h#I am too much like the 'monsters' on display to be comfortable at the human Spirit's Eve festival, but I don't mind if you wish to go.$s",
                "winter_Krobus": "The darkness this time of year is very soothing. If only it were warmer!",
                "winter_1": "Today the season of darkness begins, and all of us shadow people increment our ages.#$b#How many years have I lived? {{Query: 525 + {{Year}} }}!$h#$e#Oh, I am not so old. The venerable Seigneur Hiedra counts nearly twenty millennia!",
                "winter_2": "The fire makes such lovely dancing shadows on the walls. I could watch them for hours.",
                "winter_3": "@, would you help me make a 'blueberry tart'? I wish to bring Linus a birthday gift, but I'm still having trouble with human cooking.",
                "winter_5": "...",
                "winter_8": "You'll have to go to the ice festival without me, @... it is too cold and too bright.#$b#I'm sorry. But I want to hear all about it when you come home!",
                "winter_12": "...",
                "winter_13": "@! I've made an incredible discovery! It is called a 'hot shower'...$l#$e#Why are you laughing?$s",
                "winter_15": "Merchant travelers from distant lands... how fascinating. Perhaps if I find a warm enough coat to wear...",
                "winter_17": "Magnus Rasmodius celebrates his birth today. Perhaps I'll bring him some fresh void essence for his studies.",
                "winter_19": "...",
                "winter_26": "...",
                "winter_28": "Thanks for letting me stay here, @. I'm looking forward to another great year!$h", //tweak - we are not doing him a favor, this is a mutual relationship
                "spouseRoom_Krobus": "#$c .5#We're so physically different that it's a challenge to live together, isn't it?#$e#I hope the humidity here isn't bothersome to you. We both have to compromise in order to live together!",
